title: Group Therapy: He Won't Call Her His Girlfriend
description: A listener has a problem with a newer relationship she's in.  Basically the guys she's dating doesn't want to have the title of "boyfriend" and "girlfriend" yet but they do post about each other on Facebook and do a ton together.
